Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
451 Belmont Avenue offers the opportunity of buying a prime Kewdale industrial property with buildings totaling 2,370sqm* on 4,543sqm* of land at well below replacement cost.

Located near the Perth Airports, accessible via Leach Highway and Tonkin Highway and only 8 kilometres* south-east of the Perth CBD.

The property consists of a substantial office/factory of 2,370sqm* with the office being 226sqm* and factory 2,144sqm*.

The offices are fully air-conditioned and partitioned. A generous amount of parking is located along the Belmont Avenue frontage.

The factory has a truss height of 5 metres* and is constructed of a combination of brick and asbestos walls and metal clad and asbestos roof.

CBRE has been appointed by KordaMentha as the agent for the Mortgagee in Possession to market this property For Sale. Price upon application.

Prospective purchasers are invited to call either Geoff Fraser on 0413 624 000 or Warick Irving on 0413 863 335.

33 Miles Road, Kewdale comprises a rare 1.65Ha offering positioned directly across from the Kewdale Freight Terminal within proximity to the Perth Domestic Airport and Perth’s major road network. 

Miles Road is dual carriage providing access from the recently upgraded Leach Highway, through to Kewdale Road. Other major companies located nearby include Coca-Cola Amatil, Toyota, Sadleirs, Simon National Carriers and Staples.

The property is improved with a combination of office, workshop and canopy improvements totalling some 2,263sqm* across numerous freestanding buildings.  The balance of the site comprises some 13,390sqm* of good quality bitumen paved laydown area, secured with a key card gated entry, electric perimeter fencing and a back to base security alarm system.

KEY FEATURES:
•	Office 1: 439sqm*
•	Office 2: 50sqm*
•	Workshop 1: 178sqm*
•	Workshop 2: 458sqm*
•	Canopy 1: 757sqm*
•	Canopy 2: 381sqm*
•	Total site area: 16,500sqm* 
•	Situated on the 36.5m oversized restricted access network
•	Easy access to Abernethy Road, Tonkin, Roe & Leach Highways
•	Proximity to Perth Airport and Kewdale Freight Terminal
•	Covered Washdown Bay
•	Electric perimeter fencing
•	Key card gated entry
•	Security alarm system (back to base)

The property is strategically positioned at the intersection of Kewdale and Miles Roads providing easy access to Abernethy Road, Tonkin, Roe & Leach Highways.  The sites strategic location and vast hardstand area makes this a prime laydown yard for a major transport and logistics operator requiring direct access to the Kewdale Freight Terminal and Perth Airport.

For further information or to arrange a viewing please contact the exclusive leasing agents.
